headline: Lennar Corporation Debuts North River Farms, Offering Five Home Collections with Large Homesites in Amenity-Rich Master-Planned Community in Oceanside, Ca
summary: Lennar announced the start of sales for North River Farms, a new master-planned community of single-family homes and ample amenities in Oceanside. With model homes set to open in early summer,...
